sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client
    participant API as Backend
    participant Speech as Speech Service

    Note over Client, API: 1. Create Session
    Client->>API: POST /session
    API->>API: Check quota + create pending
    API-->>Client: sessionId

    Note over Client, API: 2. Start Session
    Client->>API: POST /start
    API->>Speech: /start (business limits)
    Speech-->>API: webrtcUrl
    API-->>Client: webrtcUrl

    Note over Client, Speech: 3. WebRTC Handshake
    Client->>API: POST /offer
    API->>Speech: Proxy SDP
    Speech-->>API: SDP Answer
    API->>API: Session → active
    API-->>Client: SDP Answer

    Note over Client, Speech: 4. Real-Time Session
    Client-->>Speech: Direct WebRTC media
    Speech-->>Client: AI response
    Speech->>Speech: Track usage

    Note over Speech, API: 5. Close Session
    Speech->>API: POST /api/close
    API->>API: Deduct quota → inactive
    API-->>Speech: OK